or radiation line driving where\nquasar outflows are governed by the SED, which itself results from the\naccretion flow and hence depends on both the SMBH mass and accretion rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 20:33:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
