ns more accessible for education and research. Koma is expected to be\nused for designing and testing novel pulse sequences before implementing them\nin the scanner with Pulseq files, and for creating synthetic data to train\nmachine learning models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 20:10:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
