 is easily implementable as a post-process of\nZND profiles and provides fast estimates of the cell width, length and reaction\ntime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Jan 2023 08:02:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 18:50:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 11:28:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-07"}
